videos.headline: Storey, Pearson link up for Western Kentucky TD
videos.description: Ty Storey flicks the ball to Jahcour Pearson, who runs into the end zone for a 17-yard Western Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Storey, Pearson link up for Western Kentucky TD) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: WMU's Ali comes up with 88-yard pick-6
videos.description: Kareem Ali intercepts Ty Storey's pass and returns it 88 yards for a Western Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (WMU's Ali comes up with 88-yard pick-6) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Wassink finds Bussell for WMU TD
videos.description: Jon Wassink makes a short throw to DaShon Bussell who brushes off defenders and runs into the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Wassink finds Bussell for WMU TD) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Storey's patience leads to WKU TD
videos.description: Ty Storey remains patient and then finds Lucky Jackson in the end zone for a 5-yard Hilltoppers touchdown, tying the game at 17-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Storey's patience leads to WKU TD) 2019/12/30
